title.narrative: WAPP APL 2 - OMVS Felou Hydroelectric Project

description.narrative: The project development objectives are to (i) augment the supply of low cost hydroelectricity from the OMVS Power System to the national utilities of Mali (EDM), Mauritania (SOMELEC) and Senegal (SENELEC); and (ii) develop a nucleus of a well-functioning, cooperative, power pooling mechanism for the West Africa Power Pool (WAPP) Zone B Organisation Pour la Mise en Valeur du Fleuve Sénégal (OMVS) Countries of West Africa.
